Doc,<br><br>
Read carefully and try to understand, please.  We haven't abandoned the PTSD, but are only searching untouched ground for the cause or the protective process that helped some get through.<br><br>
The clinical approach doesn't always help.  Science and understanding marches on and only through risk may be achieve.  Feel free to join us in that risk.  We may all learn something.  There is more to come.<br><br>
Cook is telling the basis for his faith which some of us feel can not be approached separately.  His experiences are his voice and the images are more powerful for us if we maintain an open mind and see the stories for what they are.<br><br>
Questions about what we are doing angers no one.  Just remember, we look for the wounds on our soul where we can find them.<br><br>
Ed and I have taken this path on the road which Ed began.<br><br>
Join us.<br>

